CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 3, 1965, pg. 5, reads: "Slimnastics Classes - Classes will begin immediately at the Centre Avenue Branch YMCA, in slimnastics, for all interested ladies. Those enrolled may use the modern heat cabinet, bicycle, rowboat machine and the swimming pool.  Classes will begin at 7:30 pg. M. on Monday evening.  For further information, call Spenser Watkins, physical director, at 621-1762.  in photograph are (left to right ) Cecil Reive, Beverly Gray, Delores Parker, Marie Riley, Pat Reive, Carolyn Dickerson and (kneeling Mrs. Alfreda Tyson, instructor. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Carolyn Dickerson, Beverly Gray, Delores Parker, Instructor Alfreda Tyson, Marie Riley, Cecil Reive, and Pat Reive, posed in shoulder stands in "Slimnastics" class at Centre Avenue YMCA
